facts and news&#8214;, available from www.iut.nu/HabitatDay/2011/FactsNews_Daniela.pdf. 
</p>
<p> 23 See, for example, Robert M. Buckley and Jerry Kalarickal, eds., <i>Thirty Years of World Bank Shelter 
Lending: What Have We Learned?</i> (World Bank, 2006), pp. 30-31. 
</p>
<p> 24 See, for example, A/HRC/22/46/Add.2. 
